snippet.title: Tom and Mimi
snippet.description:
Hey, Welcome To My Channel

This Channel is dedicated to My Cats.


My Pets

- I'm owned by 3 cats, Tom (black & white), Mimi (white & ginger) & Prince (British shorthair kitten). This channel will be full of clips of my cats, 


Tom 

- Colour : Black & White 
- Breed : Domestic Shorthair 
- Male 
- Born : May 2014 
- Brought Home : 27/12/2014


Mimi 

- Colour : White & Ginger 
- Breed : Domestic Shorthair 
- Male
- Born : 22nd November 2014 
- Brought Home : 01/01/2015


Prince

- Breed : British Shorthair 
- Colour : Blue Silver Tabby  
- Male
- Born : 15th April 2020 
- Brought Home : 9th July 2020


Where do these cats live ? 
They live in Blackburn, Lancashire, England 


Products/Equipment i use: https://www.amazon.co.uk/shop/tomandmimi/list/3ILEFNAKFLHYE


Copyrights *** Please do not re-upload my videos without my permission ***


Contact Us: tom_mimi@outlook.com
